TableContextTimeStampAfterTable: {6841=On 7/27/2012, the development team released a list of content that will be unavailable after the transition to Final Fantasy XIV: A Realm Reborn including several of the achievements, particularly those related to the Seventh Umbral Era storyline and involving the current maps. These are marked with an asterisk *.}
textAfterTable: Let the Bodies Hit the Floor Defeat 100000 enemies. 30 Headpiece: Butcher's Crown La Noscea Big Game Hunter* Defeat the notorious monsters Barometz, Slippery Sykes, Gluttonous Gertrude, Bomb Baron, Unknown Soldier, Great Buffalo, and Old Six-arms. 10 -- Black Shroud Big Game Hunter* Defeat the notorious monsters Queen Bolete, Alux, Jackanapes, Sirocco, Phaia, Haughtpox Bloatbelly and the Prince of Pestilence. 10 -- Thanalan Big Game Hunter* Cactuar Jack, Elder Mosshorn, Daddy Longlegs, Kokoroon Quickfingers, Nest Commander, Bardi and Pyrausta. 10 -- Coerthas Big Game Hunter* Defeat the notorious monsters Uraeus, Splitfire and Downy Dunstan. 10 -- Mor Dhona Big Game Hunter* Defeat the notorious monster Dodore. 10 -- Shposhae Big Game Hunter* Defeat the notorious monsters Shearing Sheridan, Giant Remober and the Lone Coeurl. 10 -- Bane of the Tribes* Defeat the notorious beastmen Lozol Totoloq the Decapitator, Flamefist Ahlygg Roh, and Third Order Patriarch Zu Ga. 10 -- Notorious Monster Hunting* Defeat 25 notorious monsters.
